2026-05-13T17:38:08.3171267Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-13T17:38:08.3172091Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-13T17:38:08.3173110Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T17:38:08.3173949Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T17:38:08.3174775Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-13T17:38:08.3175582Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-13T17:38:08.3176399Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-13T17:38:08.3177353Z 33    -->
